name: Escape Zone
description:
Trapped, distracted, locked. My soul began to come out of the trap of the negative zone that has become a part of my life, many problems that are very painful but very useful in our lives.

This piece is a form of collaboration with MetaFunnel for the #MFdrop event. Collect this and get the chance to grab the prize!
